Vimya
========================================================================

A Vim plugin to execute the contents of a Vim buffer, the current visual
selection, or a single command in Autodesk Maya. Both MEL and Python
scripts are supported, Maya's log can optionally be opened in a separate
preview window or tab in Vim.


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION
------------------------------------------------------------------------

More information can be found in the documentation located in the 'doc'
folder, and in vim.org's script section:

   <http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2626>

The Git repository and bug tracker are hosted at Bitbucket:

   <https://bitbucket.org/goeb/vimya/>


